README for HTTP::WebTest::XMLParser

ABSTRACT

This module is a Parser for WebTest definitions in XML
format, based on example script from XMLReport 

More detail is available from the module's documentation:

  perldoc HTTP::WebTest::XMLParser

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

  HTTP::WebTest (version 2.x, install before this one!)
  XML::SAX (known to work with version 0.12)

If you plan to write test definitions back as XML, the following 
modules are additionally required:

  XML::Writer (also needed for Webtest XMLReport)
  B::Deparse (only if the webtests contain CODE sections)

